South African Labor Union Rejects Eskom’s Wage Offer as Talks Resume Today

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-07-21T06:03:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-21/south-african-labor-union-rejects-eskom-s-wage-offer-as-talks-resume-today.html
South Africa ’s National Union of
Mineworkers rejected Eskom Holdings Ltd.’s offer for a 5.5
percent wage increase, the union said in an e-mailed statement
today.  Talks will resume today, said the union, which is demanding
a 16 percent increase.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Carli Lourens at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net  